@startuml
title Classic Chain of Thoughts (CoT)

actor User
participant LLM

User -> LLM : Task: "Solve complex problem X"

note right of LLM
LLM generates:
1. Plan (steps 1-5)
2. Step 1 reasoning
3. Step 2 reasoning
4. Step 3 reasoning
5. Final answer
**All in one response**
end note

LLM -> User : Plan:\n1. Do A\n2. Do B\n3. Do C\n\nStep 1: ...\nStep 2: ...\nStep 3: ...\n\nAnswer: Y

note right of User
Problem: LLM can "fit" 
reasoning to pre-decided 
answer (answer-first bias)
end note

@enduml
